    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pan-fried salmon</strong> over the <strong>creamy pesto veg</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped basil </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
